  "description": "Unsafe methods to write even faster code! Users are expected to know what they are doing and improper usage can\nresult in corrupting scene state and segfaults.",
  "title": "Class GameObjectMarshal",
  "content": "<h1 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Ecs.Marshalling.GameObjectMarshal' data-commentId='T:Alis.Core.Ecs.Marshalling.GameObjectMarshal' id='Alis_Core_Ecs_Marshalling_GameObjectMarshal'>Class GameObjectMarshal    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/4_Operation/Ecs/src/Marshalling/GameObjectMarshal.cs#L39'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h1>\r\n <div class=\"facts text-secondary\">\r\n<dl><dt>Namespace</dt><dd><a href='Alis.Core.Ecs.Marshalling.html'>Alis.Core.Ecs.Marshalling</a></dd></dl><dl><dt>Assembly</dt><dd>Alis.dll</dd></dl>\r\n</div><p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Ecs.Marshalling.GameObjectMarshal.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Unsafe methods to write even faster code! Users are expected to know what they are doing and improper usage can\nresult in corrupting scene state and segfaults.</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>public static class GameObjectMarshal</code></pre><h4 class='section'>Inheritance</h4><dl class=\"typelist inheritance\"><dd>\r\n<div>\n<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object'>object</a>\n</div>\n<div>\n<a href='Alis.Core.Ecs.Marshalling.GameObjectMarshal.html'>GameObjectMarshal</a>\n</div>\n\r\n</dd></dl><h4 class='section'>Inherited Members</h4><dl class=\"typelist\"><dd>\r\n<div>\n<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object.equals#system-object-equals(system-object)'>object.Equals(object?)</a>\n</div>\n<div>\n<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object.equals#system-object-equals(system-object-system-object)'>object.Equals(object?, object?)</a>\n</div>\n<div>\n<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object.gethashcode'>object.GetHashCode()</a>\n</div>\n<div>\n<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object.gettype'>object.GetType()</a>\n</div>\n<div>\n<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object.memberwiseclone'>object.MemberwiseClone()</a>\n</div>\n<div>\n<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object.referenceequals'>object.ReferenceEquals(object?, object?)</a>\n</div>\n<div>\n<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object.tostring'>object.ToString()</a>\n</div>\n\r\n</dd></dl><h2 class='section'>Remarks</h2><p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Ecs.Marshalling.GameObjectMarshal.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The APIs in this class are less stable, as many depend on implementation details.</p>\n<h2 class='section'>Methods</h2><h3 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Ecs.Marshalling.GameObjectMarshal.EntityId(Alis.Core.Ecs.GameObject)' data-commentId='M:Alis.Core.Ecs.Marshalling.GameObjectMarshal.EntityId(Alis.Core.Ecs.GameObject)' id='Alis_Core_Ecs_Marshalling_GameObjectMarshal_EntityId_Alis_Core_Ecs_GameObject_'>EntityId(GameObject)    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/4_Operation/Ecs/src/Marshalling/GameObjectMarshal.cs#L53'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h3>\r\n <p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Ecs.Marshalling.GameObjectMarshal.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Gets the raw entityID from an <xref href=\"Alis.Core.Ecs.GameObject\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref></p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>public static int EntityId(GameObject gameObject)</code></pre><h4 class='section'>Parameters</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt><code>gameObject</code> <a href='Alis.Core.Ecs.GameObject.html'>GameObject</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</dd></dl><h4 class='section'>Returns</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt> <a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.int32'>int</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Ecs.Marshalling.GameObjectMarshal.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The integer entityID</p>\n\r\n</dd></dl><h3 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Ecs.Marshalling.GameObjectMarshal.GetWorld(Alis.Core.Ecs.GameObject)' data-commentId='M:Alis.Core.Ecs.Marshalling.GameObjectMarshal.GetWorld(Alis.Core.Ecs.GameObject)' id='Alis_Core_Ecs_Marshalling_GameObjectMarshal_GetWorld_Alis_Core_Ecs_GameObject_'>GetWorld(GameObject)    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/4_Operation/Ecs/src/Marshalling/GameObjectMarshal.cs#L47'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h3>\r\n <p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Ecs.Marshalling.GameObjectMarshal.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Gets the <xref href=\"Alis.Core.Ecs.Scene\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> for an <xref href=\"Alis.Core.Ecs.GameObject\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref>. Does not check if the <xref href=\"Alis.Core.Ecs.GameObject\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> or\n<xref href=\"Alis.Core.Ecs.Scene\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> is alive.</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>public static Scene GetWorld(GameObject gameObject)</code></pre><h4 class='section'>Parameters</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt><code>gameObject</code> <a href='Alis.Core.Ecs.GameObject.html'>GameObject</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Ecs.Marshalling.GameObjectMarshal.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The <xref href=\"Alis.Core.Ecs.GameObject\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> to get the <xref href=\"Alis.Core.Ecs.Scene\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> for.</p>\n\r\n</dd></dl><h4 class='section'>Returns</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt> <a href='Alis.Core.Ecs.Scene.html'>Scene</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Ecs.Marshalling.GameObjectMarshal.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The <xref href=\"Alis.Core.Ecs.Scene\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> the <code class=\"paramref\">gameObject</code> belongs to, if it still exists.</p>\n\r\n</dd></dl>",
